                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Force fields interfere with a paralith\u2019s perception. A paralith takes a \u20134 penalty to attack rolls and Perception checks against a creature that has an active force field armor upgrade or energy shield gained from the mechanic trick of the same name.",
                "name": "Force Field Blindness",
